title: CTMP Mosport First Lap In-Car - The 2013 Porsche IMSA GT3 Cup Challenge By Yokohama, Rounds 7 and 8
description: Opening Lap of Round 7 of the Porsche IMSA GT3 Cup Challenge with Brett Sanberg of TruSpeed Motorsports around the Canadian Tire Motorsports Park.  Watch as Brett manages his Yokohoma tires through the opening lap chasing down Angel Benetiz Jr and Madison Snow.
